{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/HighresScreenshot002117-31.png?t=1730099526\" /><br><strong>POLYGON</strong> is a tactical multiplayer team 1st person shooter. <br>Using various weapons, you will battle with <strong>up to 32 players</strong> on large-scale maps. <br>Properly managing your arsenal and skills, you will lead your team to victory!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/ezgif.com-optimize__2_.gif?t=1730099526\" /><br><br>Team up with up to 16 players to fight in furious PvP matches. <br>Group up with your friends in the squad to bring the teamplay to another level!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/ezgif.com-optimize__3_.gif?t=1730099526\" /><br><br>A large arsenal is available \u2013 each weapon has a real prototype! <br>Choose between assault rifles, PDWs, LMGs, DMRs and Sniper rifles to find your play style. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/ezgif.com-video-to-gif__8_.gif?t=1730099526\" /><br><br>A customization system will help you to adjust your weapon to your needs. <br>Change sights, handles, muzzle devices and accessories. <br>Also, you can unlock many skins to show off on a battlefield!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/ezgif.com-resize__1_.gif?t=1730099526\" /><br><br>Jump into battle in any location: from spacious valley to narrow subway. <br><strong>Different maps \u2013 different situations!</strong><br><br>The game is constantly being improved. <br>Change the outcome of the battle using new weapons and skills. <br>Team up with friends and explore new locations.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEVELOPMENT</h2><br>Intuitive controls and 