ng-edge innovations, the Unreal engine gives the POLYGON game amazing graphics!<br><br><br><br>At the moment, the game is being developed by <strong>only one person</strong>. <br>Hi, my name is <strong>Nick</strong>! <br>Meet me and our friendly Moderators on Discord where we can help you and tell you more about the game :) <br>We also often hold various events where you can get in-game rewards.<br><br><strong>Dive into battle with POLYGON!</strong>","developers":["Redaster Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Massively Multiplayer","id":"29"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/header.jpg?t=1730099526","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257025862,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257025862/movie480.mp4?t=1716759848","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257025862/movie_max.mp4?t=1716759848"},"name":"Polygon Trailer #4 (ultra) | Tom","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257025862/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1716759848","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257025862/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1716759848","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257025862/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1716759848"}}],"name":"POLYGON","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_fr